e request payload format is not supported.'=>'不支持请求负载格式。','The requested contact form was not found.'=>'没有找到您要的联系表单。','The total size of attachment files is too large.'=>'附件文件总和太大。','There are also special mail-tags that have specific names, but do not have corresponding form-tags. They are used to represent meta information of form submissions like the submitter&#8217;s IP address or the URL of the page.'=>'还有一些特殊的邮件标签，它们有特定的名称，但没有相应的表单标签。它们用于表示表单提交的元信息，例如提交者的IP地址或页面的URL。','There are invalid mail header fields.'=>'有无效的邮件标头。','There are terms that the sender must accept'=>'有些选项发件人必须同意接受','There is a field that the sender must fill in'=>'发件人必须填写必填项','There is a field with input that is longer than the maximum allowed length'=>'一个字段输入超过最大允许长度','There is a field with input that is shorter than the minimum allowed length'=>'一个字段的输入短于最小允许长度','There is a possible empty field.'=>'有一个可能的空字段。','There was an error deleting the contact form.'=>'删除联系表单时出错。','There was an error saving the contact form.'=>'保存联系表单时出错。','There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.'=>'发生错误，请稍后再试。','There was an error uploading the file.'=>'上传文件时出错。','There was an unknown error uploading the file.'=>'上传文件时出错。','This contact form contains CAPTCHA fields, but the necessary libraries (GD and FreeType) are not available on your server.'=>'这个联系表单包含CAPTCHA域，但是您的服务器上没有必须要用到的库（GD and FreeType）。','This contact form contains CAPTCHA fields, but the temporary folder for the files (%s) does not exist or is not writable. You can create the folder or change its permission manually.'=>'这个联系表单包含CAPTCHA域，但包含文件(%s)的临时文件夹不存在或者没法写入。您可以创建文件夹或者手动修改权限。','This contact form has file uploading fields, but the temporary folder for the files (%s) does not exist or is not writable. You can create the folder or change its permission manually.'=>'此联系表单有文件上传字段，但文件的临时文件夹(%s)不存在或不可写。您可以手动创建文件夹或更改其权限。','This contact form is available only for logged in users.'=>'此联系人表单仅供已登录地用户填写。','This field has a too earl